                    <h1 class="title citation_title" itemprop="name">FedCPS: A Dual Optimization Model for Federated Learning Based on Clustering and Personalization Strategy</h1>
                                   
                    <p class="authors citation_author">
                        Zhen Yang<sup>1</sup>, Yifan Liu<sup>1,2,*</sup>, Fan Feng<sup>3</sup>, Yi Liu<sup>3</sup>, Zhenpeng Liu<sup>1,3</sup>                    </p>

                    <p class="affiliation">
