                                            <p class="Corresponding">

                        * Corresponding Author: Yifan Liu. Email: <img style="vertical-align: middle" alt="email" src="https://www.techscience.com/psh.php?mailname=lyf@hbu.edu.cn" />  

                        </p>
                    
                                        <p class="cite-info">
                       <i>Computers, Materials &amp; Continua</i> <b>2025</b>, <i>83</i>(1), 357-380. <a href="https://doi.org/10.32604/cmc.2025.060709">https://doi.org/10.32604/cmc.2025.060709</a>                    </p>
                    <p class="article-date">
